# guid

Generates a GUID.

### Examples

```javascript
guid();
// => "0153a717-3ba2-b1ac-67f1-49db6551a28d"
```

Returns **[string][1]** of guid.

**Meta**

*   **version**: 1.0.0

[1]: https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String
